title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Oscar Guzman Flies Again
content:
Take to the air, land, and sea to help Oscar Guzman in this latest set of action-packed missions.

Steal more than what’s been asked of you, and you’ll be rewarded generously. It’ll be no easy feat but should prove worth it once you can finally call that Titan 250 D yours.

You’ll need to own the McKenzie Field Hangar which can be purchased on the Maze Bank Foreclosures website. The missions will then be available from the laptop in the office.
